structure.unit: LICENSING OF MOTOR VEHICLES, OPERATORS, AND TRAILERS

law.history: Repealed 2003 Ky. Acts ch. 74, sec. 3, effective June 24, 2003. -- Amended 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 48, sec. 16, effective July 15, 1998; and ch. 565, sec. 5, effective July 15, 1998. -- Created 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 366, sec. 5, effective July 15, 1996.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Special license plates for youth soccer.
metadata.lrc-note: (7/15/98). This section was amended by 1998 Ky. Acts chs. 48 and 565 which do not appear to be in conflict and have been codified together.
